casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Lautzenheiser.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Lautzenheiser (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(No. 91-510 Submitted April 9, 1991 Decided April 17, 1991.)

The resignation of Patricia Lautzenheiser as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
